Nighal 14: I have finally found the secret of the stone. It allows a person
	to enter another's dreams. I fail to see how this can help, but it is
	my last chance. I will sleep, sleep until someone can try it on me. I
	have no way to tell how long that will be, and it may be that I may
	die before I am saved. I locked the apparatus so that the spirits
	could not steal the stone. Three twists to the left and a press of
	the button in the middle will release the stone.
	
The diary ends here. You take specific note of the directions to release
the stone.

